sequenceDiagram
    actor U as Usuario
    participant F as Frontend (React)
    participant A as API (Next.js)
    participant DB as Supabase (PostgreSQL)

    U->>F: Arrastra ticket a "Done"
    F->>A: PATCH /api/tickets/123 {status: "Done"}
    A->>DB: UPDATE tickets SET status='Done' WHERE id=123
    DB-->>A: OK (Ticket actualizado)
    A-->>F: 200 OK (Datos del ticket)
    F-->>U: Actualiza UI (Ticket visible en "Done")
